availablePathosToStake(address).details: Return the amount of Pathos that can be staked on Pool

params._taoId: The TAO ID of the Pool

availablePathosToStake(address).return: The amount of Pathos that can be staked

params._ethosLotId: The ID of the Ethos Lot

lotLogosAvailableToWithdraw(bytes32).return: The amount of Logos available to withdraw

ownerEthosLotIds(address,uint256,uint256.details: Get list of owner's Ethos Lot IDs from `_from` to `_to` index

params._nameId: The Name Id of the Ethos Lot's owner

ownerEthosLotIds(address,uint256,uint256.return: list of owner's Ethos Lot IDs

ownerTotalEthosLot(address).return: Total Ethos Lots the owner has

params._status: The status to set. true = start. false = stop
params._taoId: The TAO ID of the Pool
